BugInstance.message: org.apache.shardingsphere.sqlfederation.original.OriginalSQLFederationExecutor.setParameters(PreparedStatement, List): 2nd parameter 'params' could be declared as java.lang.Iterable instead
This use of java/sql/Connection.prepareStatement(Ljava/lang/String;)Ljava/sql/PreparedStatement; can be vulnerable to SQL injection (with JDBC)
